 BLACKPINK 的 Rosé 表示，她最好的歌曲是在“Hot Ones”中“生活非常糟糕”时创作的https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-best-songs-writing-when-life-bad-3810765?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=blackpink-rose-best-songs-writing-when-生活糟糕Gladys YeoFri, 08 Nov 2024 06:11:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3810765 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Rosé blackpink 歌曲创作" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这就是我最喜欢创作的地方，你可以把不太好的东西[然后把它]变成美丽的东西”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-best-songs-written-when-life-bad-3810765">BLACKPINK 的 Rosé 发帖称，她最好的歌曲是在《Hot Ones》中的“生活非常糟糕”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上时创作的。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Rosé blackpink 歌曲创作" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/blackpink-rose-songwriting-081124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont