0-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特</a>透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joaquin-phoenix">杰昆·菲尼克斯</a>在<em>《角斗士》</em>拍摄过程中差点退出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><b>《小丑：双人舞》评论：Lady Gaga 在一部挑衅性的监狱音乐剧中大放异彩</b></a></li></ul><p>在接受《 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/11/07/movies/ridley-scott-gladiator-ii-denzel-washington.html?unlocked_article_code=1.YE4.1mR7.JwtMYMTdvqqJ&amp;smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;referringSource=articleShare" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>纽约时报》</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-ii"><em>采访</em></a>时，斯科特被问到菲尼克斯退出项目的名声。据导演介绍，这是长期以来的一个特点。在拍摄第一部<em>《角斗士》</em>电影时，斯科特透露菲尼克斯临阵退缩，想退出电影。</p><p>菲尼克斯对是否要出演这部电影犹豫不决，导致联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-crowe">罗素·克劳</a>指责他“不专业”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3782561" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782561" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782561" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new.jpg" alt="华金·菲尼克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/joaquin_phoenix_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782561" class="wp-caption-text">华金·菲尼克斯于 2023 年 11 月 20 日在西班牙马德里出席《拿破仑》首映式。 （卡洛斯·阿尔瓦雷斯/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> “他穿着王子的服装说，‘我做不到。’”我说：“什么？”拉塞尔（克罗）说，‘这非常不专业，’”斯科特向《<em>纽约时报》</em>解释道。然而，斯科特最终说服菲尼克斯留下并完成了这个项目——他后来因此获得了奥斯卡提名。</p><p> “我可以扮演一个哥哥或爸爸的角色。但我是华金的好朋友。<em>角斗士</em>一开始对我们俩来说都是一场火的洗礼，”斯科特说。他和菲尼克斯后来在 2023 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/napoleon-review-ridley-scott-joaquin-phoenix-3547971"><em>《拿破仑》</em></a>中重聚。</p><p>菲尼克斯退出项目的传闻直到最近才被曝光，当时有消息称，菲尼克斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joaquin-phoenix-drops-out-of-todd-haynes-gay-romance-film-days-before-filming-was-to-begin-3782559">退出了托德·海恩斯领衔的一部同性恋爱情电影，就在该片定于八月开拍的前几天</a>。菲尼克斯与海恩斯和乔恩·雷蒙德一起创作了这部电影的剧本。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joaquin-phoenix-wasted-todd-haynes-time-on-cancelled-gay-romance-says-producer-3796620">这部电影后来被完全取消</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3549921" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3549921" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3549921" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix.jpg" alt="《拿破仑》中的杰昆·菲尼克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Napoleon-Joaquin-Phoenix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3549921" class="wp-caption-text">华金·菲尼克斯在 Apple Original Films 和哥伦比亚影业院线上映的《拿破仑》中饰演拿破仑·波拿巴。图片来源：索尼/凯文·贝克</figcaption></figure><p>在退出托德·海恩斯的电影后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-mcavoy">詹姆斯·麦卡沃伊</a>透露，菲尼克斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-mcavoy-claims-joaquin-phoenix-abandoned-split-role-two-weeks-before-filming-3793709">在开拍前两周也同样“放弃”了<em>《分裂》</em>中的主角</a>，导致麦卡沃伊在最后一刻登上了这个现在的标志性角色：“我认为他放弃了这个角色。”他们开始拍摄前两周。这真的是最后一刻了。”</p><p>菲尼克斯最近主演了<i>《小丑：双人舞》(Joker: Folie à Deux)</i> ，该片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-folie-a-deux-scores-record-low-audience-score-for-comic-book-movie-3799985">在票房上经历了一段艰难的时期</a>，首映周末在国内票房收入约为 4000 万美元（3050 万英镑），远远低于华纳兄弟的票房。原始预测。现在，在电影上映几周后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-folie-a-deux-already-coming-out-online-end-of-month-3802929">该片于 11 月 4 日在数字家庭上映</a>，由于财务困难而加速上映。</p><p> <i>《NME》</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522">在对<i>《Folie à Deux》</i>的四星评论中</a>写道：“与原版电影一样，这部电影自始至终看起来都很华丽，电影摄影师劳伦斯·谢尔（Lawrence Sher）大力运用色彩并创造出一些美丽的图像——亮点包括一些人的俯视镜头。雨伞（参考雅克·德米 1964 年的音乐剧<i>《瑟堡的雨伞</i>》）和亚瑟在牢房里点燃香烟的令人惊叹的灯光框架，就像一个精美插图的漫画书面板。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/quentin-tarantino-thinks-joker-folie-a-deux-was-todd-phillips-way-of-saying-fuck-you-to-hollywood-3807713"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><figure id="attachment_3790597" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3790597" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3790597" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Gaga_Phoenix_Joker_Folie_A_Deux.jpg" alt="小丑" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Gaga_Phoenix_Joker_Folie_A_