0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/quincy-jones-rashida-jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/quincy-jones-rashida-jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/quincy-jones-rashida-jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>拉什达·琼斯向她已故的父亲和传奇制片人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯</a>致敬——请参阅下面这位演员对她父亲的评价。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="650" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386"><b>昆西·琼斯，1933-2024：眼中闪烁着光芒打破界限的超级制片人</b></a></li></ul><p>本周早些时候（11 月 4 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">传奇制片人昆西·琼斯 (Quincy Jones) 在家人陪伴下去世，享年 91 岁的消息传出</a>。随着他的去世，人们纷纷向这位已故偶像表示敬意。虽然拉什达在昆西去世时与家人发表了一份联合声明，但她现在公开向昆西致敬。 </p><figure id="attachment_3810751" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3810751" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3810751" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rashida-jones-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3810751" class="wp-caption-text">拉什达·琼斯和昆西·琼斯。图片来源：Michael Kovac/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>这位演员分享了一张自己婴儿时被昆西抱着的照片。她写道：“我父亲成年后一直在夜间活动。他从高中开始就一直坚持“爵士乐时光”，并且从未回头。小时候，我会半夜醒来寻找他。毫无疑问，他会在房子的某个地方作曲（老派，用笔和乐谱）。他永远不会把我送回床上。当他继续工作时，他会微笑着把我搂在怀里……对我来说，世界上没有比这更安全的地方了。</p><p> “他是一个巨人。一个图标。文化转变者。天才，”她继续说道。 “对我父亲的所有准确描述，但他的音乐（以及他所有的作品）都是他爱的渠道。他就是爱。他让他遇到的每个人都感到被爱和被看见。这是他的遗产。</p><p> “我很幸运能够近距离体验这种爱。我会想念他的拥抱和亲吻以及无条件的奉献和建议。爸爸，成为您的女儿是我的[荣幸]。你的爱永远存在。”</p><p>请参阅下面 Rashida Jones 的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCFbXEbzIkG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="ht